vw - Video Watch

USAGE:
    vw <video-id> [-castnow] [-castnow=device]

DESCRIPTION:
    Watch a downloaded video. Searches for video by ID (can be a
    substring), plays it, allows adding comments, and then moves
    it to watched or retains it based on user choice.

ARGUMENTS:
    video-id
        ID of video to watch (can be a substring, required)

OPTIONS:
    -castnow
        Send video to a chromecast device

    -castnow=device
        Send video to specified chromecast device

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-videos-video-player CMD
        Video player command (default: system default)

    -conf-videos-download-path PATH
        Path where videos are stored

EXAMPLES:
    vw abc123
    vw abc123 -castnow
    vw abc123 -castnow=living-room-tv
